---
title: Carolina's Chorizo Penne Carbonara with Garden Salad
description: Carolina is our beloved colleague, who brings a dash of Spanish flair to our office. She's the inspiration for this creamy and delicious pasta, which uses chorizo instead of the classic bacon for an extra dose of flavour and fun that the whole family will love. Thanks, Carolina!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/carolina-s-chorizo-penne-carbonara-44cb9f28.jpg
